fields.status_extended: Login to the AWS Console. Choose your account name on the top right of the window -> My Account -> Alternate Contacts -> Security Section.

check_metadata.risk: AWS provides customers with the option of specifying the contact information for accounts security team. It is recommended that this information be provided. Specifying security-specific contact information will help ensure that security advisories sent by AWS reach the team in your organization that is best equipped to respond to them.
